==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Igloo
<hw>Ig"loo</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An Eskimo
snow house.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A cavity, or excavation, made in
the snow by a seal, over its breathing hole in the ice.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ignatius bean</ent>⟦br⟧
